{"tid":843681,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不只退休！ 馬雲早已放棄阿里巴巴所有權轉交給5位新所有人","createTime":"2018-10-01T10:29:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-01T11:03:35.000Z","uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1a8948b9fbb379d33fae502e313ad08821064317","tid":843681,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T10:29:05.000Z","msg":"不只退休！ 馬雲早已放棄阿里巴巴所有權...<br />\n<br />\n2018-10-01 14:16:00<br />\n<br />\n〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕中國電商阿里巴巴創辦人馬雲在日前宣佈將退休後，阿里巴巴今（1）證實，馬雲已放棄阿里巴巴的主要法律實體所有權。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">《金融時報》報導，據阿里巴巴7月向美國證券交易委員會（SEC）提交的文件，顯示馬雲和阿里巴巴聯合創使人謝世煌，已放棄阿里巴巴中國業務相關的「可變權益實體」（Variable Interest Entity，VIE）所有權，並將所有權轉交給5位新所有人，這5人的身份目前尚未披露。</span><br />\n<br />\n阿里巴巴今證實此消息，並稱馬雲放棄該公司的VIE所有權，是為了減輕行政負擔。但馬雲仍維持阿里巴巴股東，以及36位合夥人之一的身份。《鉅亨網》指出，放棄VIE所有權的馬雲，將不再對阿里巴巴有重要控制權。<br />\n<br />\n阿里巴巴屬於大多數中國在海外上市的「可變權益實體」公司之一，實體通常允許中國技術公司從海外實體獲得投資。<br />\n<br />\n馬雲則在9月10日宣佈，將在1年內卸任阿里巴巴執行董事長，並將工作交給阿里巴巴集團執行長張勇。<br />\n<a href=\"http://ec.ltn.com.tw/m/article/breakingnews/2567064\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Fm%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2567064&d=gyT6NCKs291rbtPbCDDifv1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=b1a7ebd0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Fm%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2567064&h=237e1a04\" target=\"_blank\">http://ec.ltn.com.tw/m/article/breakingnews/2567064</a>"},{"pid":"15e617673310c28f8e3f7937c701741b521825ff","tid":843681,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T10:30:32.000Z","msg":"搵咁多我都退啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c07d36efe6ff83bc9b1423e2b77f48a666a6cd5","tid":843681,"uid":208376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T10:32:35.000Z","msg":"黨批準左？馬雲而家係邊？"},{"pid":"d430a5b2622ec49b141168f3dde885340e5f7d36","tid":843681,"uid":38523,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"15e617673310c28f8e3f7937c701741b521825ff","tid":843681,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T10:30:32.000Z","msg":"搵咁多我都退啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T10:32:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 早走早著<br />\n大家心照啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed5a7a1663c71c4dbd0f9e62ffb2b9e2c59b4f0d","tid":843681,"uid":46737,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T10:33:30.000Z","msg":"黨員點會開名"},{"pid":"49a26882194c96c02861967870a28448a2dc658f","tid":843681,"uid":134323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T10:39:46.000Z","msg":"別讓馬雲跑了"},{"pid":"4e81f9afa003ff0ad8bde62aff2d993de6c203de","tid":843681,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49a26882194c96c02861967870a28448a2dc658f","tid":843681,"uid":134323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T10:39:46.000Z","msg":"別讓馬雲跑了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T11:03:35.000Z","msg":"應該無得走 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做國內有錢人"}]}